View as web page <[[{{system.viewAsWebpageLink}}]]> Save the date! MEET Nokia at NANOG 75 If you’re into peering, meet us at NANOG 75! San Francisco, CA, February 18th to 20th 2019 Meet us at NANOG 75 <[[http://www.cvent.com/events/nanog-75/event-summary-948222eca5834bc2b7a679399063e724.aspx]]> to find out how to take control of your peering edge.
- See demos on automated peering engineering & insight-driven DDoS mitigation - Hear Igor Giangrossi discuss 5G from an IP engineer’s perspective <[[https://pc.nanog.org/static/published/meetings/NANOG75/daily/day_4.html#talk_1875]]> - Meet our experts at the Beer ‘n Gear from 6-8pm on Tuesday evening View the event page and register at NANOG 75 <[[http://www.cvent.com/events/nanog-75/custom-116-948222eca5834bc2b7a679399063e724.aspx]]> © {{my.CopyrightYear}} Nokia.
